# Security Policy

## Reporting a vulnerability

If you believe you've found a security vulnerability in {{ project_name }},
please report it privately — **do not open a public issue**.

Email: **{{ author_email }}** with subject `SECURITY: {{ project_name }}`.

We'll acknowledge receipt within 3 business days and coordinate a fix and
disclosure timeline with you.

## Supported versions

Only the latest released version receives security updates.
